    Specifies possible values for the alignment of the contents of this run in relation to the default appearance of the run's text. This allows the text to be repositioned as subscript or superscript without altering the font size of the run properties.(指定此管路内容相对于管路文本默认外观的对齐方式的可能值。这允许将文本重新定位为下标或上标，而不更改运行属性的字体大小。)
